fields.name: Yokohoma

Light Truck Tires: These tires are built for small trucks used in delivery and transport operations in urban environments. They offer high durability and wear resistance1.

Yokohama tires are known for their advanced technology and innovation, making them a reliable choice for various driving needs.

fields.name: Semperit Speed-Grip 5
fields.description: The Semperit Speed-Grip 5 is a high-performance winter tire engineered for passenger vehicles. Replacing its predecessor, the Semperit Speed-Grip 3, this tire is designed as a multi-talented offering that combines exceptional winter capabilities with reliable performance on dry roads.

fields.name: Star Performer Stratos UHP 221031560
fields.description:
The Star Performer Stratos UHP is a high-performance tire designed for ultra-high performance (UHP) vehicles. Here are some key features:

Excellent Traction: Provides strong grip on both dry and wet surfaces.
Enhanced Stability: Offers improved handling and stability at high speeds.
Durability: Built to last with a robust construction.

This tire is suitable for those looking for a balance of performance and reliability

fields.name: Star Performer Stratos UHP 221031646
fields.description:
The Star Performer Stratos UHP with the model number 221031646 is a winter tire designed for high performance. Here are some key details:

Size: 225/45 R17
Load Index: 94 (indicating the maximum load capacity)
Speed Rating: V (up to 240 km/h)
Type: XL (Extra Load, meaning it can carry heavier loads)
Season: Winter

This tire is known for its good performance in winter conditions, providing reliable traction and stability on snowy and icy roads

fields.name: Superia Bluewin HP 15580 R13 79T winter tyre
fields.description:
The Superia Bluewin HP 155/80 R13 79T is a winter tire designed for passenger vehicles. Here are some key features:

Size: 155/80 R13
Load Index: 79 (indicating the maximum load capacity)
Speed Rating: T (up to 190 km/h)
Type: Winter tire with M+S marking and snowflake symbol
EU Tyre Label: D for fuel efficiency, D for wet grip, and 68 dB for noise level12.

This tire is known for its reliable performance in winter conditions, providing good traction and stability on snowy and icy roads.

fields.name: Superia Bluewin HP 16570 R13 79T winter tyre
fields.description:

Size: 165/70 R13

Speed Rating: T (up to 190 km/h)
Type: Winter tire with M+S marking and snowflake symbol
EU Tyre Label: E for fuel efficiency, E for wet grip, and 69 dB for noise level.

This tire is known for its reliable performance in winter conditions, providing good traction and stability on snowy and icy roads.

fields.name: UNIROYAL WinterExpert 03631470000
fields.description:
The UNIROYAL WinterExpert with the model number 03631470000 is a winter tire designed to handle challenging winter conditions. Here are some key features:

Size: 155/65 R14
Load Index: 75 (indicating the maximum load capacity)
Speed Rating: T (up to 190 km/h)
Type: Winter tire with M+S marking and snowflake symbol
EU Tyre Label: C-D for rolling resistance, B-C for wet grip, and 71-73 dB for noise level12.

This tire is known for its excellent handling performance on wet roads, thanks to its new tread pattern design and Shark Skin Technology, which reduces the risk of aquaplaning2. It also offers good performance on snow and ice, making it a reliable choice for winter driving.
